726151f-a.title: Queens: Bell Boulevard - 35th Avenue
726151f-a.text:
Bell Boulevard (foreground), at the N.W. corner of Thirty-fifth
Ave., showing Murphy's Hotel,also called Boulevard Hotel. In 1934
the house was moved west of its site and a gasoline station was placed
on the old site. Both places were then operated by Samuel Golden.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
